SUMMARY:IMPROMPTU LI - Hills around Speedwell Forge (26R)
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\n## Details\n\nRide Leader
 : Bruce Black\n\nIt will be a little chilly but warming up throughout the 
 ride. It still should be a good day for a ride and some food. Time to star
 t getting in some early season climbing but not too much.\n\nAn enjoyable 
 ride from Lititz exploring the hills around Speedwell Forge. We will stop 
 at the Lititz location of New Holland Coffee Shop for food/beverage. The p
 ace will be 14 - 16 mph average. Multiple regroup points (like 4 or 5). Pl
 ease park in the upper parking lot of the library.\n\nThis ride is a socia
 l ride\, but cyclists are not expected to stay in one group. Cyclists may 
 pedal at their own comfortable paces. Please be supportive of the other cy
 clists to avoid anyone biking alone or being dropped off the back of the l
 ast group.\n\nCue and Ride with GPS links:\n[LI - Hills around Speedwell F
 orge (26R)](https://ridewithgps.com/routes/54567966?privacy_code=U5ABRfuVw
 YacNFGNifwY41RUt5fl5zJx)\n\nHelmets are mandatory\; please also plan to br
 ing 1-2 water bottles\, and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\,
  pump/CO2 inflator).\nBeing a Meetup Member does not mean you are a club m
 ember. Use this link to join the club.\n[https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net
 /content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net
 /content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148)\nYour RSVP is your agreement to a
 bide by the club's Code of Conduct [https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/c
 ontent.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984](https://lancbikecl
 ub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984
 )\nand Rules of the Road\n[https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.as
 px?](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=
 257148&module_id=325159)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3141855
 74/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260408T194046Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260408T194046Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
